
Iteration:yenileme

1) While loop a programing construct that allows you to repeatedly check a condition and execute code. 
With the while loop we can execute the code as long as a condition is true. 
(while döngüsü ile bir koşul doğru olduğu sürece kodu çalıştırabiliriz.)

As long as i is less than 6, the code will work.

There are some points that we need to consider when using the while loop.
When we use the while loop, we should not forget the increment or decrement part.
If we forget this, the code goes into a forever loop.

